    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Critical, Level 4+ </p><p>You've practiced making your jutsu more difficult to avoid, learning techniques that grant you the following benefits: </p><p>• When a creature would make a saving throw against damage from a Ninjutsu or Genjutsu you cast and they would fail the saving throw by 5 or more, increase the damage by the rank of jutsu Cast.</p><p> (D-Rank: +5, C-Rank: +10, B-Rank: +15, A-Rank: +25, S-Rank: +25).</p><p>• When a creature would make a saving throw against a Ninjutsu or Genjutsu you cast that inflicts a condition and they would fail by 5 or more, regardless of the jutsu's effect, the next time they would successfully remake the saving throw or succeed the check needed to remove the condition (if applicable), they instead do not remove the condition.</p><p></p>",
